We need to determine the main business revenue item from the transactions data. In our file the “Sale” transactions represent revenue from the sale of products and have an “after_tax_amount” value that represents the net revenue from that sale.

Step 1. Identify the rows with type “Sale” and read their “after_tax_amount” values. In our dataset these sale rows are:

Step 2. Sum these amounts:

  989756.10

Step 3. The main business revenue item is therefore 13,815,672.74.
